    <div class="container">


        <div class="row align-items-center my-5">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded mb-4 mb-lg-0" src="images/smart.jpg" alt="">
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <h1 class="font-weight-light">Smart Farming & Harvest</h1>
                <p>Smart farming is a management concept focused on providing the agricultural industry with the
                    infrastructure to leverage advanced technology – for tracking, monitoring, automating and analyzing
                    operations.</p>
                <a href=""><button  class="btn-smart">Get Started</button></a>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="card text-white holder-info my-5 py-4 text-center ">
            <div class="card-body ">
                <p class="text-white m-0 ">"Agriculture is our wisest pursuit, because it will in the end contribute
                    most to real wealth, good morals & happiness."</p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">State-wise Report on cultivation</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Agriculture is the science, art, and practice of cultivating crops, livestock, and other renewable resources. Professionals in the field of agriculture are called agriculturists, they provide advice to farmers and farm employees. Farms and agribusinesses are the core of the agriculture industry.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a href="/biharcropdetail/show"><button  class="btn-smart">More Info</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">Share  Soil Snaps</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Share you soil snap and get detail/reports on it.A Farming library for the farmer to get all
                            important agriculture information
                            related to crops, agriculture cycle,
                            agriculture field preparation and more.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a href="/soildetails/new"><button  class="btn-smart">More Info</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">Browse Latest News</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Instant access to news report with
                            all required categories expected in agricululture
            and farming India ranks second worldwide in farm outputs. As per 2018, agriculture employed more than 50% of the Indian work force and contributed 17–18% to country's GDP.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a href="/news?page=1&limit=5"><button class="btn-smart">More Info</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">Current Weather</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Instant access to weather report with
                            temp, RH, rainfall possibility, expected
                            wind speed & its direction in the set
                            preferred location</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a href="/weather"><button class="btn-smart">More Info</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">Reports on MSP (Minimum Selling Price)</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Farmers can get instant access to
                            minimum selling prices for their
                            produce, market status and prevailing
                            trade prices along with quantities.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a href="/msp/show"><button class="btn-smart">More Info</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 mb-5">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title">Our Advisors </h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Our Advisors are ready to answer you
                            and support you in your way of keeping
                            your crops healthy. You can connect with
                            our crop experts through Q&A section</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a href="/experts/showexpert"><button href="#" class="btn-smart">More Info</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


        </div>


    </div>



  
